# This directory stores automated backups

## Backup Configuration

- **Frequency**: Daily at 2 AM (production)
- **Retention**: 30 days (configurable)
- **Format**: PostgreSQL SQL dump

## Manual Backup

```bash
./scripts/backup.sh
```

## Restore

```bash
# Stop n8n
docker-compose -f docker-compose.production.yml stop n8n

# Restore
cat backups/n8n_backup_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS.sql | docker exec -i n8n-postgres-prod psql -U n8n_prod n8n_production

# Restart
docker-compose -f docker-compose.production.yml start n8n
```

## Important

- Backup files are **NOT** committed to Git (see .gitignore)
- Store backups securely off-site
- Test restore procedures regularly
